u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City AM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"The Turnover\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"your weekly roundup\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"sport business news\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She apologised for her actions and stated that she had \\\"let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\\\"\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9701777613416657, \"rank\": 0.030738470388276273, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her actions\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video has not been publicly released but Sportsbeat were told the incident related to an alleged video showing \\\"Dujardin repeatedly whipping a horse on the legs during a lesson\\\".\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sportsbeat\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SportsBeat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The video\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"the incident\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"an alleged video showing\", \"from\": 1347